data.description: Welcome to Brookstone Lakes in Conyers, Ga where you will find this beautiful brick face listing in a new constructions neighborhood. This LARGE corner lot listing was recently built in the year 2022 and since closing on the home in 2023, the owners have made a few upgrades of their own! These updates include, front yard landscaping, upgraded lighting & backsplash, new kitchen faucets and additional pendant lights making your kitchen more unique than any other kitchen in the neighborhood. Your open concept kitchen and living area also provide easy access to a spacious deck, perfect for intimate settings on warm summer nights! This is a smart home and comes with all of the industry leading smart home products to keep you connected to the place you value most. One of the rooms have been made into an office where a wall shelf unit has been added. The large primary bedroom suite offers walk-closets and double vanity sinks. This home IS one of the 3 homes in the neighborhood that have a full daylight walkout basement and since closing the owners have partially finished it now providing a second space perfect for entertaining family and friends!! The energy in this home is unmatched! Please request your tour via showing time to put yourself in this NEWLY BUILT & UPGRADED home!! JUST LISTED!! More photos coming soon!!!
